:QUOTE
Your first digital product teaches you more than any course ever will.

:INFO
Selling Digital Products on Gumroad
Gumroad lets you sell ebooks, templates, courses, and downloads directly to your audience. Low friction setup, built-in payments, and a simple storefront make it a strong starting point for solo creators building digital revenue.

:COUNTER.half
0 Fees
To get started on Gumroad
|
:COUNTER.half
10%
Platform fee per sale

:PATH
Create Your Product
Define the format: PDF, ZIP, video, or course. Write for a specific problem your audience already has.

:PATH
Price With Confidence
Research comparable products. Price based on value delivered, not hours spent. Test with a launch discount.

:PATH
Market Without Ads
Use your existing content and email list. Share the story behind the product. Let early buyers leave reviews.

:CHECKLIST
Launch Checklist
[ ] Write product description that focuses on outcomes
[ ] Add a cover image that looks professional at thumbnail size
[ ] Set up a thank you page with next steps
[ ] Enable ratings and reviews
[ ] Create a short launch email to your list

:NOTE
Gumroad sends payouts weekly. Connect your bank early so you are not waiting on a payout delay after your first sale.

